**Key pattern detection markers:**
- `[INST]` / `[/INST]` - Mistral/Llama2 instruction markers
- `[SYSTEM_PROMPT]` - Mistral v7 system prompt marker
- `[AVAILABLE_TOOLS]` - Mistral v3 tool support marker
- `<<SYS>>` - Llama2 system message marker
- `<|im_start|>` - CharML format marker

